comments.body:
We could const the parameter and locals to obviate which one we're writing:
```suggestion
template <ByteType B>
void WriteLE16(B* ptr, const uint16_t x)
{
    const uint16_t v{htole16_internal(x)};
    memcpy(ptr, &v, 2);
}
```

